channel.title: Mr Mooo‚Äôs Custom AP Challenge! (RESULTS OUT!)
channel.description: This was inspired by @anon73773654 so thank you! I said this as a joke but I think some people could produce some cool stuff! The challenge: Make your own AP (sound pack) by using sounds from other packs but with heavy automation so they sound like new sounds! Make names for all your sounds and label them. Include at least one drum kit. Make a short song with your new sounds (like a demo song). You can have as many sounds as you want. Terms and conditions: The song has no time limit, but it is recommended that the length length is around thirty seconds. You must name your new sound pack with your name in the title (e.g the sound of Mr Mooo). You don‚Äôt have to post this to soundcloud, you can if you want, but make sure you send me the project link (so I can see the individual instruments). The entries are due in on February 16th (in 3 weeks in my NZ time). I‚Äôm pretty sure that covers it, so have fun and good luck! üòâ üêÆ Edit: also, a sound pack is really good when all the sounds are kinda linked. Melodic percussion has tropical sounds and signature pianos are all piano sounds. The best ones in my opinion will not be the packs with just random sounds, but the packs with linked sounds .
